flowRoot.flowPara: Thank you for joining us in exploring the wonderful world of engineering. Enclosed you should find all the parts for building a CopyCat drawing robot arm. Please check that the contents of your box match the list below. Please email support@narwhaledu.com if there are any discrepancies.
Assembly instructions and a parts list with more detailed information can be found at

<http://narwhaledu.com/copycat>. We recommend not assembling the kit until the course begins on February 28th, 2014. You will be sent an invitation to join the course to the email you provided in the kickstarter survey around noon EST on that day. Please keep the box for storing your assembled kit and other supplies, or recycle it.
1 small washer, 2 big washers, 2 big nuts
